title: Ep179 Pro Wrestling Crimes
description: This week, the gals slip on their spandex and frogsplash into the wild world of theatrical wrestling. Topics include Lucha Libre melodrama, one very fatal flashback, and a locker room stabbing that only gets worse from there. Shotgun a can of McBride Sisters She Can Rosé in dramatic fashion, retire your "King of Dong Style" shirt, and tune in for Pro Wrestling Crimes. For a full list of show sponsors, visit www.wineandcrimepodcast.com/support
